## Goal
- Discover currently active Indian government-backed technical competitions (hackathons, innovation challenges, AI/ML challenges, cybersecurity/CTF competitions, defence innovation challenges) via iterative web reconnaissance.

## Constraints & Preferences
- Output strict JSON only; no markdown, no commentary.
- Reject incubators, accelerators, startup grants, R&D calls, fellowships, procurement, workshops, conferences.
- Only include opportunities with active registration/submission (open forms, current deadlines).
- Deduplicate against previously discovered candidates.
- Prioritize official government domains (gov.in, nic.in, mygov.in, sih.gov.in, idex.gov.in, indiaai.gov.in) over Tier 3 sources.
- Follow strict discovery order: refresh high-priority portals → extract active challenge URLs → validate open/active signals → filter → deduplicate.
- Never hallucinate deadlines, ministries, prizes, URLs, or SDG alignment.

